the world. Your way will not even be comprehensible within yourself. You
will be living from mystery ‚Äî moving from mystery to mystery to mystery
‚Äî uplifted and carried by something that brings a satisfaction and a
fulfillment to the depth of your soul, far beyond anything you can now
imagine.</p>

