<blockquote>
  <p>Boy, you are really quite a master, you know? You really deserve all
this adulation. Why don‚Äôt you keep ten percent of it for yourself?</p>
</blockquote>

<p>A master accepts the Love offered, the gratitude offered by those whom
his or her teachings have touched and gives it all to God, recognizing
that of themselves these things could not have been done. I learned,
too, to be tempted. And when those would come to me who were sick found
