occurs, <em>you must practice discipline and vigilance by remembering
humility always, until you are remembering it with every breath</em>.</p>

<p>And why? If you are living in this world, and feel that no one looks up
to you, no one takes you as authority, there is only one reason. You
have resisted the Truth of your being, and through denial have pushed
God‚Äôs Light away out of your fear, your deep-seated fear, that you might
